/common/youtube.png\" alt=\"タツミ訪問看護 youtube\"></a></li>\n</ul> \n</div> \n </nav>\n <!-- /.header-gnav -->\n</header>\n<!-- ========= / header END ========= -->\n\t\n\n<!-- ========= sub keyvisual ========= -->\n<div class=\"sub-keyvisual\">\n <div class=\"sub-keyvisual-text\">\n  <h2>訪問看護のお仕事の流れ</h2>\n </div>\n <!-- /.keyvisual-text --> \n</div>\n<!-- ========= / sub keyvisual END ========= --> \n\n<!-- ========= main ========= -->\n<main class=\"main bg-pattern subpage\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"bread_crumb_list\">\n<ul class=\"bread_crumb\" typeof=\"BreadcrumbList\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\">\n<!-- Breadcrumb NavXT 7.4.1 -->\n<li class=\"level-1 top\"><a href=\"https://www.medi-p.jp/recruit\">ホーム</a></li><li class=\"level-3 sub tail current\"> 訪問看護のお仕事の流れ</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t\n<section class=\"sub-content\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"visit-nursing-box bg-white-box\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"ttl-02 c-lgreen\">最初はみんな未経験。<br class=\"pc-disp\" />“訪問看護”というお仕事に触れてみませんか。<br class=\"pc-disp\" />あなたが活きる環境を全力でバックアップします。</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"visit-nursing-box bg-white-box\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"ttl-02 flow\"><small>flow</small>訪問看護<br>お仕事の流れ</h3>\r\n  <div class=\"flow-content flex flex-reverse\">\r\n    <div class=\"flow-content-box-wraper\">\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span> 9:00<br />\r\n            ステーションに出勤<br />\r\n            朝のミーティング\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span> 9:20<br />\r\n            鞄を持って出発！\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span> 9:30～10:30<br />\r\n            Aさん宅で療養指導<br />\r\n            （慢性肝臓病の食事指導、血圧管理など）\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span> 10:40～11:40<br />\r\n            Bさん宅で服薬管理<br />\r\n            （内服薬の管理と、インスリン注射もサポート）\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span> 12:00<br />\r\n            ステーションに戻る\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"flow-content-figure\">\r\n      <h4>午前中</h4>\r\n      <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.medi-p.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/medi-p-recruit/assets/images/one-day/img_flow01.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"flow-content flex\">\r\n    <div class=\"flow-content-figure\">\r\n      <h4>午後</h4>\r\n      <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.medi-p.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/medi-p-recruit/assets/images/one-day/img_flow02.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"flow-content-box-wraper\">\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span>\r\n            12:00<br />\r\n            お昼休憩\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span>\r\n            13:00<br />\r\n            出発\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span>\r\n            13:15～14:15<br />\r\n            Cさん宅で排痰・吸引\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span>\r\n            14:30～15:30<br />\r\n            Dさん宅でNPPV<br />\r\n            （非侵襲的陽圧換気療法）のケア\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span>\r\n            15:40～16:45<br />\r\n            Eさん宅で療養指導<br />\r\n            （慢性肝臓病の食事指導、血圧管理など）\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span>\r\n            17:30<br />\r\n            ステーションに戻り、所長に報告・相談\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flow-content-box\">\r\n        <div class=\"flow-content-text\">\r\n          <p class=\"flow-content-text__title\">\r\n            <span></span>\r\n            18:00<br />\r\n            報告書作成、OC利用者の申し送りを行い、夕礼後帰宅\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"flow_bnr flex\">\r\n  <div class=\"flow_bnr_img\">\r\n    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.medi-p.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/medi-p-recruit/assets/images/one-day/img_flow04.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"flow_bnr_cont\">\r\n    <p>訪問時の流れ</p>\r\n    <a href=\"https://www.medi-p.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/medi-p-recruit/assets/pdf/houmon_flow.pdf\" target=\"_brank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">詳細をクリック</a>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\n</section>\n</main>\n<!-- ========= / main END ========= -->\n  <section class=\"main-link\">\n    <div class=\"foot-link flex\">\n      <div class=\"item\"> <a href=\"https://www.